      "rationale": "Three hexahedral meshes (0.8 M, 3.1 M, 11.4 M cells) were generated with refinement ratio r ≈ 1.5. Richardson extrapolation applied to NIH at the worst-case operating point (6 L/min, 3500 RPM). GCI_fine = 3.7%, apparent order p = 1.94, confirming asymptotic convergence. Discretization error criterion satisfied at Gradation 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
